  "commit_message": "Pin vendored compact_index to a reviewed commit\n\nDefaulting the fetch ref to master made rake setup non-reproducible: an\nupstream change in rubygems.org could alter the compact_index code the\nartifice runs without any corresponding change here, turning unrelated\nPRs red with no commit in this repository to bisect against. Pin to\nrubygems/rubygems.org#6504 and keep REF as an override for testing newer\nrevisions.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>",
